content: /*<![CDATA[*/ $('#title').html($('meta[name=map-description]').attr('content')); /*]]>*/ Google Cloud Identity integration official release July 1, 2024—Google Cloud Identity integration with Trend Vision One is now officially available. Seamlessly integrate with Google Cloud Identity to enhance your security visibility and response with streamlined access, management, and risk. Go to Workflow and Automation → Third-Party Integration to set up the integration. For more information, see Google Cloud Identity integration.
